data.text:
Michael Wenzel, 28, of Loveland, passed away March 31, 2012. He was born on January 8, 1984 in Boulder, CO to Michael Wenzel and Tammy Pierce.

Michael worked with his dad working iron. He loved to ride his motorcycle, play golf, darts and 4 wheeling. Before he was hurt, he loved sports like, skiing, snowboarding, camping, fishing and mixed martial arts. His friends were his life.

He is survived by his parents, Michael Wenzel and Tammy Pierce and step father, Sam Harding of Loveland; aunt, Diane Larson (Darrell) and her daughters, Jessica Frank, Kristina Frank and her two year old daughter, Bryleigh Frank; grandparents, Michael and Patricia Wenzel of Longmont, CO; uncle, Mark Wenzel (Barb) of CA; step brothers, Dustin Nelson (Candice) and two year old Tanner Nelson of Windsor, CO.

Michael was preceded in death by his brother, Matthew Wenzel; grandparents, Mary Bowman and Keith Duncan; aunt, Debbie Swallow.
